Type: Package
Package: GeoDist
Title: Constrained distance calculation and associated geotools
Version: 0.1.0.8000
Author: Sébastien Rochette
Maintainer: Sébastien Rochette <sebastienrochettefr@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows the calculation of
    distances that are constrained by frontiers, islands, mountains, ...
    These distances are then implemented in classical geotools like
    kriging with a modified version of geoR functions.
License: GPL-3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.0),
    geoR
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    graphics,
    gstat,
    igraph,
    magrittr,
    methods,
    parallel,
    raster,
    readr,
    rlang,
    snow,
    sp,
    stats,
    tcltk,
    utils
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: 
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
